{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-06", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-06</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> Medtronic Data Breach Exposes Over 3.8 Million People<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">醫材大廠美敦力資料外洩事件，影響逾380萬人</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Medical device giant Medtronic disclosed a hacking incident from April that compromised the personal data of more than 3.8 million people, the company told customers last week.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">醫療器材大廠美敦力上週通知客戶，4月發生的駭客入侵事件導致超過380萬人的個資外洩。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177091\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Google and FBI Disrupt NetNut Residential Proxy Network<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Google與FBI聯手打擊NetNut常駐代理網路，涉及逾200萬台裝置</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Google partnered with the FBI, Lumen and other organizations to disrupt NetNut, a large residential proxy network believed to involve at least two million home internet-connected devices.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Google宣布與美國聯邦調查局、電信業者Lumen等單位合作，針對大型常駐代理網路NetNut採取行動，該網路涉及至少200萬台家用連網裝置。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177098\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> JetBrains Patches Critical Flaws in Hub Identity Platform<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">JetBrains修補開發環境身分管理平臺Hub重大漏洞</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">JetBrains fixed three critical vulnerabilities in JetBrains Hub, its identity and access management platform, which could allow account takeover and privilege escalation if left unpatched.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">JetBrains近日修補身分與存取管理平臺Hub的三項重大漏洞，未更新恐導致帳號接管與權限提升，影響整個開發環境的帳號管理。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177100\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> Armored Likho Hackers Target Governments and Energy Firms with BusySnake Stealer<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">駭客團體Armored Likho鎖定政府機關與能源產業，散布竊資軟體BusySnake</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Kaspersky discovered a targeted phishing campaign by the APT group Armored Likho, attacking government agencies and power sector organizations in Russia, Brazil and Kazakhstan using a Python-based info stealer.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">卡巴斯基發現駭客組織Armored Likho針對俄羅斯、巴西與哈薩克的政府機構與電力部門，利用Python打造的竊資軟體BusySnake Stealer竊取帳密與Cookie資料。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177101\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> Taiwan Launches Second Product Bug Bounty Program, Focusing on Local Software<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">資安署啟動第二屆產品資安獵捕活動，臺灣軟體產品成核心目標</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Taiwan's National Institute of Cyber Security is launching its second product vulnerability hunting event, shifting focus from ICT hardware to homegrown software products.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">國家資通安全研究院即將舉辦第二屆產品資安漏洞獵捕活動，相較首屆聚焦硬體產品，此次轉型聚焦臺灣軟體產品。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177092\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> Google Cloud Expands Confidential Computing to Protect AI Inference and Prompts<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Google Cloud擴大機密運算版圖，強化AI推論與提示詞加密防護</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Google Cloud announced expanded confidential computing services, including preview Confidential G4 VMs with Nvidia Blackwell GPUs and open-source Prompt Encryption SDKs to protect AI prompts and responses.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Google Cloud宣布擴大機密運算服務，包括搭載Nvidia Blackwell GPU的Confidential G4 VMs預覽版，以及用於加密AI提示詞與回應的開源SDK。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177093\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> Microsoft Teams Tightens Control Over External Meeting Bots<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Microsoft Teams加強控管外部機器人，需會議組織者核准才能加入</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">As AI meeting assistants and transcription tools proliferate, Microsoft announced a new policy requiring meeting organizers to approve external bots before they can join Teams calls.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">隨著AI會議助理與轉錄工具普及，微軟宣布新政策，要求外部機器人加入Teams會議前須經會議組織者核准。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177095\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> What Is Mistral AI? Everything to Know About the OpenAI Competitor<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Mistral AI是誰？這家OpenAI競爭對手的重點整理</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Mistral AI, known for its open-source AI models, has raised significant funding since its 2023 founding, with the ambition to put frontier AI in everyone's hands.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">以開源AI模型聞名的Mistral AI自2023年成立以來已募得大量資金，目標是讓每個人都能使用前沿AI技術。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/04/what-is-mistral-ai-everything-to-know-about-the-openai-competitor/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Some Wealthy American Families Are Letting AI Teach Their Kids<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">部分美國富裕家庭讓AI取代傳統學校教育子女</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">While most Americans distrust AI, some wealthy families are turning to AI-driven schools like Forge Prep instead of traditional education for their children.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">儘管大多數美國人不信任AI，一些富裕家庭仍選擇讓Forge Prep等AI驅動的學校取代傳統教育。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/961505/wealthy-ai-schools-alpha-forge-prep\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Amazon Will Stop Accepting New Customers for Mechanical Turk<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">亞馬遜將停止Mechanical Turk新客戶申請</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Amazon is winding down new customer onboarding for Mechanical Turk, signaling what may be the final days of its crowdsourced labor marketplace.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">亞馬遜將停止接受Mechanical Turk平臺的新客戶申請，這可能意味著這個群眾外包勞動市場即將走向終點。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/05/amazon-will-stop-accepting-new-customers-for-mechanical-turk/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}